Franck Ribery turned down a move to Real Madrid in 2009 . 
  The Frenchman says he was told he was as important to Bayern Munich as Lionel Messi is to Barcelona . 
  Real wanted him after he fell out with then-head coach Louis van Gaal . 
  Real were willing to pay for him but he was convinced of his importance to the club . 
  He has won four Bundesliga titles and the Champions League with Bayern . 
 